                <div class="TermsConditionsText">
                                        <h1>Direct Energy Solar Professional Referral Network Agreement</h1>
                                         <p class="intro">Once a Referral Partner has completed the free, no obligation registration process and has been verified as a participant in the program, an introduction will be sent via email.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span>When a registered Referral Partner submits a Qualified Lead to Direct Energy Solar, the Referral Partner will receive a payment specified as a Qualified Lead Bonus. This money is the Referral Partner&rsquo;s to keep regardless of whether any of these leads convert to sales.</span></li>
                    <li><span>&ldquo;Qualified Leads&rdquo; shall be defined as follows:</span></li>
                    <div class="subList">
                        <ul>
                            <li><span>Customer must have had no prior contact with Direct Energy Solar</span></li>
                            <li><span>Customer owns Customer&rsquo;s property</span></li>
                            <li><span>Customer is a potential candidate for solar, as reasonably determined by Direct Energy Solar</span></li>
                            <li><span>Referral Partner has discussed Direct Energy Solar with the customer and the customer is expecting to be contacted</span></li>
                            <li><span>Partner has not shared customer&rsquo;s information with any other solar services company</span></li>
                            <li><span>Customer agrees to a sales visit to discuss the site evaluation and has a genuine interest in going solar, as reasonably determined by Direct Energy Solar</span></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <li><span>When Referral Partner&rsquo;s Qualified Lead enters into a contract for a solar power system with Direct Energy Solar, the Referral Partner receives a flat sale reward payment specified as a Sales Bonus.</span></li>
                    <li><span>Payments are aggregated and paid by check and sent via U.S. mail the month following the activity.</span></li>
                    <li><span>Qualified Leads who sign contracts for solar power systems with Direct Energy Solar may / may not  receive a discount toward their systems. Only one referral discount can be applied to any system dependent of the current Direct Energy Solar discount promotion.</span></li>
                    <li><span>Partners are entitled to compensation for initiating a relationship with a new Direct Energy Solar customer, subject to other terms of the partner program. Once Direct Energy Solar has converted a partner submitted lead to a customer, partners are not entitled to any compensation for any additional products or services sold to that customer at a later date.</span></li>
                    <li><span>Referral Partner must submit a completed W-9 form to Direct Energy Solar prior to receiving payments.</span></li>  
                    <li><span>Referral Partner should submit a company logo to assist Direct Energy Solar in creating marketing collateral.</span></li>
                    <li><span>All work for the solar power system sold will be performed by Direct Energy Solar.</span></li>
                    <li><span>Referral Partner agrees to hold the terms of the agreement confidential, including payment amounts.</span></li>
                    <li><span>Referral Partner agrees to only utilize marketing materials approved by Direct Energy Solar when promoting the program and to perform no marketing or advertising activities without permission of Direct Energy Solar.</span></li>
                    <li><span>This agreement can be terminated by either party with a written notification. Referral Partner will get paid for any Qualified Leads referred prior to the date of cancellation.</span></li>
                </ul>
<p>By accepting this agreement, you acknowledge and agree to the terms and conditions above. Direct Energy Solar will permit individuals, employer affinity programs, lead generation services, non-profit and membership affiliate organizations into the program at the sole discretion of the program manager.</p>


